title: Exiled Bot Beta v0.11c + Key (Path of Exile bot) [arMa]
description:
Actual Features

    Fully passive (no injection)!!
    Monster searching and killing
    Pathfinding and area exploring
    The bot takes flasks and chicken
    Gems leveling
    Auras handling
    Picks up orbs, gems, scrolls, and maps!
    Inventory stasher
    User can configure the items he wants the bot to pickup (rares, 6S, 5L, ...)
    Highly configurable
    Automatic game restart and zone cleaning
    Combat routines customization

Features to Come

    Maps farming
    Questing
    Crafting
    Vendoring
    Fully configurable PickIt!
    More combat customization
    Other cool things requested by the community
